features: 100% recycled SuperGrid Body Material with Blue Sign approved color dyeing process—900d x 2400d 100% recycled Polyester w/ .18mm TPE film backside and rough PU film on the frontside paired with a 1640d Polyester w/ PU coating end fabric

Integrated Shoulder Strap System—to save weight as well as for a better carry for larger volume bags, we integrated an EVA harness system directly into the bail handles for comfort and secure carry
Two Bail Handles with LockOut™ sternum strap connection
Burly #10 YKK reversed coil main compartment zipper
LockOff™ Internal Compression System keeps gear contained and under control
Side-to-Side padded body construction adds puncture and abrasion resistance for an extra level of security
Tech info screen prints for quick reference to product weights and materials
Custom Black Diamond molded zipper pullers.
